description: For sale: $299,900. Check out this beautiful 4bed/3bath custom built log home on 80 acres.  Logs were harvested from the land.  Beautiful fireplace to enjoy on those cool nights.  Lots of custom cabinets in the kitchen and laundry room.  A private balcony and jetted tub in the master, along with an open loft sitting area and walk-in closet. Enjoy the views of roaming animals from your rocking chair on the covered porch.  Must see to appreciate the beauty!!!

description:
Recently sold: $223,000. Private Homestead in the Woods: 40-acre home with amenities for self-sufficient living. Secluded home with guest house, spacious heated shop and two-car garage. Enjoy the captivating views of the park-like yard from your back deck or the comfort of the gazebo. The Master bedroom boasts a hardwood floor, walk-in closet and a private tiled bathroom. There is ample storage in the open kitchen, with a large island and a pantry, too. The home has newer roof and hot water heaters. Don't worry about the cold with the high-efficiency wood burning stove capable of heating the entire home. A new well was drilled in 2017 to service the home, and includes a Bison frost-free handpump.
 
The guest home has a bedroom, living room, sunroom, half bathroom and full kitchen. It is on a separate well which recently received a new soft-start pump for easy generator use. It has a modern wood burning cookstove for your cooking and baking needs and beautiful views of the landscaped yard.
 
There are blueberry and raspberry bushes, two mature apple trees and plenty of gorgeous perennials. Or you can enjoy foraging in the woods for wild fruits, nuts and mushrooms.
 
There is a sizeable garden area, greenhouse, new shed, 1.5 acres of pasture, and a large insulated chicken coop. Wildlife abound and deer are plentiful. Explore the mature forest from the maintained trails or take advantage of the proximity to public land, ATV trails and other recreational opportunities.
